{"tid":2092121,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國新型豬流感 G4 據報已由豬傳人    佛奇：需嚴加關注","createTime":"2020-07-03T05:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T14:15:25.000Z","uid":141151,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"200ca911cee2400731b03d9e48dfd8a07f7f4957","tid":2092121,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:05:27.000Z","msg":"中國新型豬流感 G4 據報已由豬傳人，佛奇：需嚴加關注<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2020/07/01/g4-ea-h1n1-attention/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2020%2F07%2F01%2Fg4-ea-h1n1-attention%2F&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXAjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=ffa83e1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2020/07/01/g4-ea-h1n1-attention/</a><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎（武漢肺炎、COVID-19）疫情未歇，研究人員又在中國發現新型豬流感病毒。美國白宮的新冠肺炎顧問佛奇（Anthony Fauci）指出，此一新病毒兼具 2009 年 H1N1 豬流感和 1918 年西班牙流感病毒的特徵，相當危險，必須嚴加關注。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">CNBC、紐約時報 6 月 30 日報導，中國發現的新型豬流感，名為「G4 EA H1N1」（簡稱 G4）。6 月 30 日美國國家過敏和傳染病研究所所長福奇在參議院聽證會上表示，G4 不是「立即威脅」，但是必須嚴加注意。福奇表示：「出現全新病毒變成大流行病時，通常是突變，或是基因重組和交換造成。」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">他說，G4 具備 2009 年 H1N1 病毒的特徵，也有 1918 年西班牙流感病毒的原始特徵。他警告，永遠有可能爆發另一場類似 2009 年的豬流感疫情。上述兩種病毒都相當致命，2009 年的 H1N1 豬流感，全球至少有 7 億人染疫，估計有 15.2 萬至 57.5 萬人死亡。1918 年西班牙流感導致 3 千萬至 5 千萬人死亡，殺傷力超越第一次世界大戰（2 千萬人死亡）。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中國疾病預防控制中心、世衛組織（WHO）、中國數家大學、英國諾丁漢大學（University of Nottingham）共同研究，宣布發現 G4 病毒。英國動植物衛生機構（Animal and Plant Health Agency）病毒學部門主任 Ian Brown，審閱過該篇論文。Brown 說：「要是該病毒繼續改變，可能會對人類更具攻擊性，一如 SARS-CoV-2（新冠肺炎病毒）。」<br />\n<br />\n台大醫院兒童感染科主任黃立民（Li-Min Huang）強調，接下來需要探究是否有養豬場工作者遭人類傳染此一病毒，也需了解病毒是否傳播給養豬場工作者的家人。黃立民說：「這是非常重要的研究，該病毒看來相當危險。我們需要擔心任何有可能人傳人的疾病。」"},{"pid":"b0427861e011965d3e5d9663999070303ec12e2b","tid":2092121,"uid":58209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:09:07.000Z","msg":"CLMB 美國佬又作假野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3c9c092fd355233ad825ed6f1ea8caa35d5767","tid":2092121,"uid":327228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0427861e011965d3e5d9663999070303ec12e2b","tid":2092121,"uid":58209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:09:07.000Z","msg":"CLMB 美國佬又作假野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:12:20.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n微博都沒報呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港那班廢青又在造謠"},{"pid":"0da3c826af81dd060d6192adb8b7c8dba694ea54","tid":2092121,"uid":176447,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:23:59.000Z","msg":"十四億兩腳豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2daf4468b9a214e6f31eeab5c41c9997dc1dd0e8","tid":2092121,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:24:50.000Z","msg":"新。新冠病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd2daf72ac6320d50550381abb839f60aca55bd","tid":2092121,"uid":294121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:44:43.000Z","msg":"呢條友拉得<br />\n報國安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372dc7c5a6b14caa9d4590f0980ecaf49f902a49","tid":2092121,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T12:32:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363df20f623543110a41c5a1f95a750a07e09f61","tid":2092121,"uid":61589,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T12:49:18.000Z","msg":"無證據顯示人傳人<br />\n可防可控<br />\n吹哨人造謠滋事<br />\n萬人食豬宴"},{"pid":"08ae2a2504237bedddc1ad2910e9d96effd13388","tid":2092121,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T12:50:37.000Z","msg":"G4 係我鄉下"},{"pid":"ea7ab14c7af60519224bdd96ccd5b8